# Workspace Conventions

## Plans
- All plans must be stored in `.cursor/plans/` within the repository root
- Plan files use the `.plan.md` extension
- Reference architecture: Pressboi (C:\Users\emill\Documents\GitHub\pressboi) is the canonical reference for shared patterns (comms, state machine, watchdog, homing, definition system)

## Architecture
- Fillhead and Pressboi share the same ClearCore hardware platform (ATSAME53N19A)
- Fillhead adds pinch valves, heater, vacuum, and volume-based injection on top of the shared base
- Pressboi is the newer, more refined codebase -- prefer its patterns when aligning shared functionality
